==Bundles==
Starfruit is one of the options in the {{Bundle|Dye Remixed||y}}.

==Recipes==
Starfruit is not used in any recipes.

==Buildings==
Starfruit is required to build a [[Junimo Hut]], purchased from the [[Wizard's Tower]].

